Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:08.00,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Do not shrink from the enemy!\NCrush them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押し潰せーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:11.96,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Spearmen, forward!\NWe must not lose this ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クリリャライ 前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 岸に上げてはなりません！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:19.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぶっ
