Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:26.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜえっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:27.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グワアーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふんっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.83,utaware def,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's charge forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっしゃあーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:42.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま一気に！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.00,utaware def,,0,0,0,,We must not.\NHuh?
