Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.16,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Hakuoro, we'll take your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハクオロ王！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そなたの首 貰い受ける！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.66,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
