Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええーっ！ えあーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.54,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Eruruu, stay by me.
